chunk_content: Ongoing support for PLHIV receiving ART service delivery improvement includes: clinical mentoring and supportive supervision of staff at HIV sites providing ART, support for quality improvement activities, patient tracking system support, routine support of ART M&E and reporting, commodities consumption forecasting, and supply management Guiding narrative 1. What percentage of patients are picking up their ART drugs on a quarterly basis? On a semi- questions: annual basis? 2. What percentage of patients are being seen for clinical follow-up visits on a quarterly basis? On a semi-annual basis? On an annual basis? 3. Describe differences in MMD uptake across age and sex groups and sites/SNUs.
